\chapter*{\begin{center}ABSTRACT\end{center}}

\noindent
The ``RevAI: Intelligent Social Media Monitoring and Auto Response Orchestration System'' project aims to develop an advanced platform to address the growing challenge of managing high-volume customer comments across multiple social media and e-commerce platforms. Businesses and content creators are often overwhelmed by the volume of interactions, leading to missed engagement opportunities and reduced quality of customer service.

\noindent
This project leverages modern APIs such as Meta Graph API and YouTube Data API, along with a robust backend system and powerful AI models, to create a unified dashboard. The system collects feedback from all connected platforms, stores it in a centralized database, and utilizes a scheduled workflow manager (Apache Airflow) to process the data in batches efficiently.

\noindent
An AI engine analyzes each comment’s intent, tone, and content to generate intelligent and context-aware responses based on user-defined rules. These responses are then automatically posted to the respective platforms, ensuring timely and consistent engagement.

\noindent
The RevAI platform provides an innovative solution to streamline customer interaction, deliver valuable insights, and ensure that no customer comment goes unnoticed. It enables businesses to maintain a responsive and professional online presence, improve customer satisfaction, and reduce manual effort while also offering insights into market trends and customer preferences.

